g.text: * A woolcock365.org.au acount is required to login for sending emails
* If your computer is outside of the Uni network, a VPN connection is required to connect to the API Server
Open an Excel file that contains
a list of patient first name,
last name, date of birth and email
Send a request to the API
The API server will generate links
and send requests to Microsoft Flow
